comedy.title: Comedy
comedy.description: The silliest slapstick, the sharpest satire, and everything in between. Tubi is not legally responsible for any busted guts or stitches in your side.

289827.title: Mad Money
289827.description: Noticing a flaw in security, three women employed by the Federal Reserve band together to smuggle out millions in bills slated for destruction.

300445.title: All Dogs Go to Heaven
300445.description: After being betrayed by his partner in crime, a dog cons his way out of Heaven to get revenge, teaming up with an orphan who can talk to animals.

302691.title: Killer Klowns From Outer Space
302691.description: Send in the clowns, this cult classic is back! One-of-a-kind alien invasion sci-fi featuring blood drinking alien clowns harvesting a small city.

304808.title: She-Devil
304808.description: A popular romance novelist embarks on an affair with his accountant, which proves to be the last straw for his disgruntled suburban wife.

310151.title: Sleepover
310151.description: Before their freshman year in high school, four best friends have a slumber party that turns into a life-changing adventure.

312200.title: Uptown Girls
312200.description: When her inheritance is stolen, a rock 'n' roll heiress must take a job as a nanny to an 8-year-old girl who is more of an adult than she is.

316456.title: The Spy Next Door
316456.description: A man asked to baby-sit his neighbor's children winds up having to fight off secret agents after one of the kids inadvertently downloads a secret code.

334159.title: The Return of the Living Dead
334159.description: While working at a medical supply company, two employees release a gas that raises the dead, causing the town to be overrun with flesh-eating zombies.

342067.title: Zapped
342067.description: A teenager who struggles to adjust to her new stepfamily and school receives some help when a dog training app gives her the power to control boys.

343312.title: Leprechaun II
343312.description: An evil leprechaun is determined to take the beautiful descendant of a love interest from one thousand years ago as his bride in modern Los Angeles.

356526.title: Be Cool
356526.description: Chili Palmer turns to the world of rock stars, pop divas, and hip hop gangstas when a new idea for a movie leads him into the music business.

389495.title: Legally Blondes
389495.description: Elle Woods's twin cousins deal with student politics, school uniforms, boys, and being framed for cheating at an elite California prep school.

389496.title: What's the Worst That Could Happen?
389496.description: A professional thief tries to rob a billionaire's mansion. But when the crook’s lucky ring is stolen, he vows revenge in this laugh-out-loud comedy.

394073.title: Baby Boom
394073.description: J.C. receives news that she has inherited a baby girl from a relative. After failing to get the baby adopted by another couple, the child becomes very attached to J.C., who reluctantly keeps the youngster. Eventually the child's mischief leads to a series of comical events that cost J.C. her job and her boyfriend, but lead her to invent an applesauce recipe for children that makes her a very wealthy woman.

404570.title: Heartbreakers
404570.description: A mother/daughter pair of cons set up wealthy man by marrying, seducing and then bilking them but their final con together gets far more complicated.

407968.title: What to Expect When You're Expecting
407968.description: A heartfelt comedy about five couples whose intertwined lives are turned upside down by the challenges of impending parenthood.

448412.title: Van Wilder
448412.description: His parties are legendary and his pranks are insane, but the most popular guy on campus meets his match when a gorgeous woman comes into his life.

461203.title: Instructions Not Included
461203.description: An Acapulco playboy's life turns upside down when a former fling leaves a baby on his doorstep, and he has to raise the child on his own.

466618.title: Teen Witch
466618.description: On the cusp of her 16th birthday, a high-school nobody discovers she has magical powers that may help her cast a spell on her dream guy.

469619.title: Cheech and Chong's Next Movie
469619.description: The zany, stoner twosome return for more misadventures as Cheech loses his job, deals with an angry neighbor and tries to appeal to a sexy lady.

469688.title: For Richer Or Poorer
469688.description: A couple who are in serious trouble with the IRS get the culture shock of their lives when they pretend to be an Amish couple in Pennsylvania.

472182.title: Escape From Planet Earth
472182.description: When a heroic astronaut from a blue-alien planet gets trapped on notoriously dangerous Earth, his overly-cautious brother must rescue him.

475898.title: Heathers
475898.description: When a snobbish high school clique threatens to ruin her reputation, a teenage girl teams up with a sociopath and plots to kill the cool kids.

489900.title: Jeff Dunham: Controlled Chaos
489900.description: The ventriloquist comedian provides fresh, hilarious material with his favorite puppets; Walter, Peanut, and two brand new characters.

507469.title: August: Osage County
507469.description: A dysfunctional mother’s emotional wounds against her adult children come to light as her family arrives at her Oklahoma home after a relative dies.

521035.title: Mac & Devin Go to High School
521035.description: In their senior year, two high school kids, an overachiever working on his valedictory speech, and a stoner who may never graduate, find new paths.

523598.title: Rolling Elvis
523598.description: When a 12-year-old boy and cycling fanatic skips school to watch TV, his mother’s punishment is to perform as Elvis Presley in the school talent show.

528587.title: Look Who's Talking Now
528587.description: In this third chapter of the series, it is not just the kids who are talking, when the family’s favorite canines bring love and chaos into their lives

528593.title: Look Who's Talking
528593.description: An unborn baby narrates the tale of an accountant who has an affair with a married client, then meets a cabbie, who longs to go along on her ride.

528603.title: Juwanna Mann
528603.description: After a basketball star is booted out of the NBA when his on-court antics go too far, he poses as a woman and joins the WUBA.

528629.title: Look Who's Talking Too
528629.description: The hilarious antics of a family with a smart aleck baby grows with the addition of a baby sister who is equally snarky and an undercover nightmare.

532473.title: Rolling Elvis: Sobre Ruedas
532473.description: Por faltar a clases, un amante del ciclismo de 12 años es obligado a cantar como Elvis en el colegio. En un abrir y cerrar de ojos le cambia la vida.

544023.title: The Brothers
544023.description: Engaging romantic comedy about 4 young Black men whose success in life is incomplete, a fact they face when their resident playboy gets engaged.

550792.title: Monster Family
550792.description: At a Halloween costume party, Emma Wishbone and her family fall under the curse of an evil witch who transforms them into real-life monsters.

551830.title: The Smurfs 2
551830.description: The Smurfs and their human pals must rescue Smurfette, who has been kidnapped by a sorcerer, because she knows a spell that can foil his evil plans.

552333.title: Daddy Day Camp
552333.description: Two dads apply their childcare magic to an underdog day camp and discover that teamwork, with a dash of craziness, makes for an unforgettable summer.

552975.title: Ozzy
552975.description: When his family goes on vacation, a beloved dog is dropped off at a fancy kennel, which turns out to be a canine prison that he must escape.

554542.title: School Dance
554542.description: Being a high school freshman is no walk in the park, but it’s even tougher as a teenager finds his dream girl and she has no idea he even exists.

555847.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married?
555847.description: Based on Perry's popular stage play, this is the story of a group of friends on a retreat who are about to get real about the trials of married life.

555948.title: Tyler Perry's Madea's Tough Love
555948.description: In her first animated adventure, Madea sets out to save the Moms Mabley Youth Center from being shut down by using her hilarious confrontation style.

557671.title: Grow House
557671.description: Two guys start a risky new business to pay off their crushing debt, but find that being able to smoke pot does not mean they know how to cultivate it.

563038.title: Deuce Bigalow: Male Gigolo
563038.description: A professional fish tank cleaner in desperate need of cash turns to the world's oldest profession and becomes a lover for hire.

563156.title: The Great White Hype
563156.description: A boxing promoter tries to boost the marketability of his fighter by finding the only boxer to beat the champ. Problem is, he isn't a boxer anymore.

565093.title: Baggage Claim
565093.description: Paula Patton stars as flight attendant Montana Moore, who is tired of the single life, hoping to meet the perfect man before her sister’s wedding.

569452.title: Kevin Hart: Laugh at My Pain
569452.description: The hilarious comic keeps it real by showing his Philadelphia roots, where he first started honing the skills that would make him a comedy superstar.

579298.title: Tyler Perry's Madea's Witness Protection
579298.description: The law’s takedown of a Wall Street banker who ran a Ponzi scheme is nothing compared to having to live with his family in hiding at Madea’s house!

581594.title: All About the Benjamins
581594.description: A bounty hunter’s botched capture of an inmate gets them stalked by diamond thieves who know one of them has a $60-million-winning lottery ticket.

582023.title: Woo
582023.description: After a tip from a psychic friend, a single woman in Manhattan with her own unique style has a date with a shy law clerk that he will never forget.

585058.title: Paper Soldiers
585058.description: An overeager thief joins a crew of equally inefficient burglars, in this outrageous comedy which depicts the rocky life of a criminal.

585148.title: Mallrats
585148.description: Male best friends, dumped by their girlfriends, spend the day strategizing at a local mall, in this funny, crude, and screamingly offensive offering.

586565.title: The Toy
586565.description: A spoiled son of a wealthy man begs his father to buy the friendship and constant companionship of a struggling writer, played by Richard Pryor.

589088.title: Practical Magic
589088.description: Two magical New England sisters must outwit and overcome their family curse, which dooms the men they love to die in tragic circumstances.

589111.title: The Lost Boys
589111.description: Sleep all day. Party all night. Never grow old. Never die. When a woman and her sons move to a California town, they discover the fun of vampire life.

589161.title: Class Act
589161.description: When a bookworm and a juvenile delinquent find their academic records switched on the first day of school, they use the mix-up to their advantage.

589177.title: Money Talks
589177.description: A con man, in need of protection from the cops, the mob, and his pregnant girlfriend, joins forces with a struggling TV newsman in need of a story.

589292.title: The Mask
589292.description: Jim Carrey’s superstar role as a kind and meek bank teller who gets super powers from a Nordic mask and becomes a totally s-s-s-smokin’ hero!

589380.title: Dennis the Menace
589380.description: Based on the beloved comic strip, a well-meaning but wholly destructive little boy unwittingly wreaks mayhem upon his surly next-door neighbor.

594095.title: Horrible Bosses
594095.description: The comedy smash about three co-workers who decide, after a lot of liquor, to get rid of their awful bosses and only manage to make things way worse.

603322.title: Waiting to Exhale
603322.description: Angela Bassett and Whitney Houston power this groundbreaking romantic comedy about four girlfriends in Phoenix waiting for honest love relationships.

611638.title: Son of Bigfoot
611638.description: A teen longs to know his father and sets out on the adventure of a lifetime to find out who he is- only to learn that his old man is Bigfoot!

611824.title: Luis and the Aliens
611824.description: A boy at risk of being sent to boarding school due to his neglectful Dad - and three aliens stranded due to watching too much TV - must help each other out.

618279.title: Ace Ventura: When Nature Calls
618279.description: Jim Carrey returns in this hilarious sequel as Ace Ventura, back from a spiritual quest and on the case to find a rare and sacred white African bat.

621624.title: Short Circuit
621624.description: When a lovable mechanical marvel of a robot is accidentally electrocuted, he flees his lab and lands on a young girl’s doorstep, ready for adventure

621683.title: Ace Ventura: Pet Detective
621683.description: When the mascot for football’s Miami Dolphins is stolen, a wacky detective goes undercover, underwater, and in over his head, to get his man or beast.

628023.title: The Best Little Whorehouse in Texas
628023.description: This rousing musical portrays a sheriff and a madam, who band together to save the infamous Texas Chicken Ranch from a big-city TV crusader.

630920.title: Drop Dead Fred
630920.description: Desperate for escape from her cheating husband and a life of ennui, a young woman gets an overdue visit from her impish imaginary childhood friend.

636625.title: El Diablo, El Santo Y El Tonto
636625.description: Antes de morir, un viejo hacendado le revela a su hijo que tiene otros dos hijos, a quienes deberá buscar para dividirse la herencia entre los tres.

637111.title: ATL
637111.description: Inside an Atlanta roller rink, four hip hop-loving teens face life-changing turning points as they prepare for what comes next after high school.

637112.title: El Inocente
637112.description: Un fin de año, la millonaria Mané iba a encontrarse con sus padres en Cuernavaca, pero su auto se descompuso en la carretera y ella no llegó.

638161.title: Allá En La Plaza Garibaldi
638161.description: Al quedarse huérfano, Julio va a buscar a su tía a la Ciudad de México, donde conoce a niños de la calle a quienes les han enseñado a robar.

638893.title: Deliver Us From Eva
638893.description: The formidable Eva Dandridge is considered an angel by her sisters, but their men think she’s a devil. Can a new suave player win her heart?

639245.title: El Hijo Del Pueblo
639245.description: Como no se halla en su vida de taxista ni con la gente de ciudad, se regresó a su rancho, donde accidentalmente cae una avioneta llena de gente bien.

639249.title: Hermelinda Linda
639249.description: Una bruja tiene pócimas y hechizos para rejuvenecer a las personas y para luchar contra los políticos corruptos que pretenden desalojar a sus vecinos.

641418.title: Los Hijos De María Morales
641418.description: Estos hermanos son un par de alegres parranderos, cantadores, jugadores y mujeriegos, y la única que puede aplacar sus travesuras es su severa madre.

641421.title: Tonta Tonta, Pero No Tanto
641421.description: La India Maria decide irse a vivir con una prima a la capital de México para encontrar un buen trabajo, pero surgen toda clase de complicaciones.

641484.title: Brown Sugar
641484.description: A record label producer and his longtime best friend come to the discovery that they’re in love almost immediately after one of them gets engaged.

641661.title: ¡El Que No corre... Vuela!
641661.description: Toda clase de abusos y atropellos sufre la India María en la gran ciudad, sin embargo, ella convierte todo problema en risas y alegría.

643938.title: Sor Tequila
643938.description: La India María, que es requetebuena para los deportes, se mete de monja y siempre anda metiendo la pata por querer ayudar a la gente.

646736.title: They Call Me Trinity
646736.description: A bounty hunter and his outlaw brother become the goofy gunslinging duo standing in the way of a craven landowner’s plan to run out Mormon settlers.

646737.title: Trinity Is Still My Name
646737.description: In the process of honoring their father’s dying wish to become famous Old West outlaws, a pair of gunslinging brothers turn into do-gooders instead.

652270.title: The Goonies
652270.description: A pair of brothers hope to save their house by following a treasure map and taking their friends along on a subterranean sea adventure.

654055.title: The Jerk
654055.description: Steve Martin makes his film-starring debut in the wacky comedy hit The Jerk. From rags to riches... to rags, the laughter never stops!

654077.title: Leap!
654077.description: An ambitious orphan with dreams of becoming a ballerina makes her way to the Paris Opera where she auditions for the lead in "The Nutcracker.”

654882.title: Judy Moody and the Not Bummer Summer
654882.description: Based on the hit children's book series, a third-grader makes her own fun for the summer after her initially fabulous plans don't come together.

657037.title: Land of the Lost
657037.description: Comedy genius Will Ferrell stars as a has-been scientist, who gets more than he bargained for, when his expedition takes a wrong turn into hilarity.

657079.title: Let's Go to Prison
657079.description: When Fate steers a career criminal’s plot for revenge off-course, he sends his intended victim’s kid to prison, and then joins him in the slammer.

658066.title: Riding in Cars With Boys
658066.description: Set in 1965, a 15-year-old girl with dreams of becoming a writer gets pregnant and enters a failed marriage with the baby’s drug-addicted father.

661116.title: Evil Bong
661116.description: A vintage bong transports all who hit from it to Bong World, an alternate realm where deadly, exotic strippers kill stoners with pleasure.

670228.title: The Queen's Corgi
670228.description: The British monarch's favorite dog gets lost from Buckingham Palace and goes on an adventure, finding himself at a dog fight club.

672234.title: Meet the Blacks
672234.description: After Carl Black moves his family to Beverly Hills, their arrival is timed with the city's annual purge, where all crime is legal for 12 hours.

672282.title: Jumanji
672282.description: Two children find and play a magical board game, releasing a man who has been trapped in it for decades and a host of wild and exotic creatures.

672284.title: Pixels
672284.description: An unlikely group of former '80s video game champions step up to save the world from an alien invasion in this visually spectacular action-adventure.

675108.title: Seventeen Again
675108.description: When Willie's science experiment goes awry, it sends both of his grandparents back to their youth. Can he find a way to reverse the process?

676665.title: The Death of Stalin
676665.description: Follows the wild scramble for power inside the Council of Ministers upon the sudden illness and death of Soviet dictator Joseph Stalin in 1953.

676687.title: Sleeping With Other People
676687.description: Lainey and Jake, neither of whom have a great track record with monogamy, form a platonic friendship that soon develops into something more.

676698.title: Mayhem
676698.description: The pent-up rage in an office is unleashed with the spread of a mysterious airborne virus that pits the last two uninfected against their coworkers.

676858.title: 16 Wishes
676858.description: On her 16th birthday, Abby Jensen's every wish comes magically, wondrously true until one wish too many go wrong and alters everything.

678774.title: Booty Call
678774.description: A wild comedy about two over-eager young men who are kept solidly at arm's length by their dates—a double date turned upside down and inside out!

678881.title: Paul Blart: Mall Cop
678881.description: When a shopping mall is taken over by a gang of organized crooks, it's up to a mild-mannered security guard to save the day.

680256.title: Kevin Hart: Let Me Explain
680256.description: A documentary following Kevin Hart's 2012 international standup comedy tour, which included performances in 80 cities around the globe.

682066.title: Roll Bounce
682066.description: When their rink closes down, a group of teenagers from the south side of Chicago enter the roller skating contest at a ritzy rink on the north side.

682075.title: Switched
682075.description: Tired of being bullied, Cassandra prays that her nemesis, Katie, the queen bee of social media, would know what it's like to walk a day in her shoes.

682626.title: Get Him to the Greek
682626.description: Aspiring music exec Aaron Green has just 72 hours to deliver rock legend Aldous Snow to LA, navigating a minefield of mayhem to get there.

684095.title: The Cobbler
684095.description: Tired of his life, Max the cobbler discovers a magical heirloom that allows him to turn into other people and see what life's like in their shoes.

689532.title: Rebound
689532.description: Suspended by the NCAA, a hotheaded basketball coach is forced to reevaluate his life when he's forced to coach a junior high team for a season.

689752.title: Drunken Master
689752.description: After a series of incidents, a mischievous yet righteous young man is sent into a brutal training program run by a master of drunken martial arts.

691608.title: Rock Dog 2: Rock Around the Park
691608.description: One year after the events of the original Rock Dog, Bodi and his friends learn that fame comes at a price when they go on their first big tour.

693353.title: 30 Girls 30 Days
693353.description: A virgin gets a chance to save his parents’ business by winning a million-dollar bet to bed nearly three dozen women inside the space of a month.

694227.title: The Rundown
694227.description: A wild action-adventure about a bounty hunter named Beck, who's searching for a rebellious mobster's son and a priceless treasure in the Amazon.

702534.title: El Cuatrero
702534.description: Con engaños, Álvaro y Mariana roban una camioneta y un caballo al ranchero Lázaro, quien los busca para recuperar sus pertenencias.

702536.title: Entre Compadres Te Veas
702536.description: Un padre y sus dos hijos deciden divertirse en el primer aniversario de la muerte de su esposa y madre y buscan aventuras en las ferias.

702670.title: Bellas De Noche
702670.description: Un boxeador retirado entra a trabajar en un centro nocturno donde se enamora de una de las bailarinas y tiene que lidiar con varios personajes.

705035.title: Garfield’s Pet Force
705035.description: A titanic confrontation of publishing universes pits comic strip and comic book heroes against a vile vixen bent on conquering Cartoon World.

707513.title: Big Stan
707513.description: Panicked he’ll be defenseless in prison, a gutless con man sentenced to hard time for fraud gets 11th hour training from a martial arts master.

710949.title: Who Made the Potatoe Salad?
710949.description: A young San Diego police officers travels to Los Angeles with his fiancée to meet her dysfunctional family and announce their engagement.

711013.title: Mid90s
711013.description: A 13-year-old spends his summer navigating a troubled home life and skating with a crew of new friends.

713166.title: Frankie Meets Jack
713166.description: Sparks fly when Frankie meets Jack, the veterinarian who rescues her dog from near death. They seem destined to be together, but there's one problem: Jack is already engaged.

714654.title: Almost Heroes
714654.description: In 1804, a habitually drunk tracker and his foppish blowhard pal lead a crew of misfits on a race to beat Lewis and Clark to the Pacific Ocean.

715989.title: Dracula: Dead and Loving It
715989.description: The vampires are loose and everyone's having a little too much fun—including the undead count himself. But professor Van Helsing is on the case.

716387.title: Keeping Up with the Joneses
716387.description: Go deep undercover in this comedy about a suburban couple who discovers their neighbors are covert spies embroiled in an international conspiracy.

716834.title: The Three Stooges
716834.description: While trying to save their childhood home, knuckleheads Larry, Curly, and Moe wind up embroiled in a murder plot and stumble into roles on reality TV.

724345.title: Identity Thief
724345.description: A hilarious blockbuster hit about an accounts representative who has one week to clear his name after a con artist steals his identity.

724351.title: Death Becomes Her
724351.description: When a jealous actress discovers an immortality treatment, she decides to take advantage of it to become young again and outshine her rival.

725274.title: Joint Custody
725274.description: A newly single father struggles to move on with life and co-parent his two kids with an ex-wife who’s determined to poison his family against him.

100000092.title: The Perfect Game
100000092.description: A retiring MLB player heads home to Mexico where he’s recruited by a ragtag team of kids to lead them to the 1957 Little League World Series.

100000194.title: I Got the Hook-Up 2
100000194.description: After a health inspector threatens to shut down a restaurant, young hustlers Fatboy and Spyda attempt to pull off a scam to save it from closure.

100000214.title: Last Action Hero
100000214.description: Jack Slater, a larger-than-life movie hero, helps a young man save his world from an assassin hell-bent on taking it over for himself.

100000215.title: Man of the House
100000215.description: A hard-edged Texas Ranger is forced to go undercover as an assistant coach to protect a group of college cheerleaders after they witness a murder.

100000217.title: Saving Silverman
100000217.description: It takes a woman with the looks of an angel and the demeanor of the devil to test an inseparable friendship three men have shared since grade school.

100000219.title: The Smurfs
100000219.description: When evil wizard Gargamel chases the tiny blue creatures out of their village, they tumble from their magical world into the middle of Central Park.

100000221.title: Smurfs: The Lost Village
100000221.description: A mysterious map sends the Smurfs on a thrilling race through a forbidden forest filled with magical creatures to find a forgotten hamlet.

100000292.title: Something Like a Business
100000292.description: An aspiring pimp struggles to make a mint after inheriting his late uncle's escort service and discovering that competition on the streets is fierce.

100000293.title: Plus One at an Amish Wedding
100000293.description: Doctor April's new romance with handsome veterinarian Jesse seems perfect—until they get invited to a wedding with the Amish family he left behind.

100000379.title: Classmates
100000379.description: A computer mixup gives two college freshman the chance to swap places but things take a turn when the switch puts them both in danger.

100000432.title: Love & Drugs 3
100000432.description: Marc tries his hardest to do the right thing for his wife and family, but he cannot seem to escape the criminal past that continues to haunt him.

100000434.title: Who's the Man?
100000434.description: In this hip-hop whodunnit, Doctor Dré and Ed Lover play two barbers-turned-policemen who find themselves investigating their friend’s murder.

100000439.title: Semi-Pro
100000439.description: In 1970s Michigan, the coach of a rag-tag basketball team pulls out all the stops to get his team into the NBA before their league dissolves.

100000440.title: Gremlins 2: The New Batch
100000440.description: The gremlins are back and they’ve taken up residence in a Manhattan skyscraper. When the rules are broken, the Big Apple will never be the same.

100000441.title: Gremlins
100000441.description: Billy’s furry Christmas present comes with three simple rules: keep him away from bright lights, don’t get him wet, and never feed him after midnight.

100000456.title: Divorce Bait
100000456.description: A happily-married suburban housewife posts on social media that she’s getting a divorce to see which of her friends try to hook up with her husband.

100000720.title: I Now Pronounce You Chuck & Larry
100000720.description: In order to receive domestic partner benefits, two straight Brooklyn firefighters are forced to improvise as love-struck newlyweds.

100000721.title: MacGruber
100000721.description: The former special forces operative and his sidekick set out on a mission to recover a stolen nuclear warhead from his sworn enemy, VonCunth.

100000724.title: Bruce Almighty
100000724.description: An encounter with God leaves a frustrated, wannabe news anchor for a Buffalo TV network with divine power and a life-altering challenge.

100000850.title: Booksmart
100000850.description: About to graduate, two best friends try to cram four years of fun into one night after spending their high school years entirely focused on studying.

100000864.title: Double Threat
100000864.description: An innocent man on a trip to scatter his brother’s ashes becomes entangled with a woman on the run from the mob after a convenience store shoot-out.

100000867.title: Howard the Duck
100000867.description: A fast-talking, cigar-chomping, beer-loving duck is transported to Earth from a parallel universe and must save the planet from an alien invasion.

100000868.title: Harry and the Hendersons
100000868.description: On the way home from a camping trip in the mountains, the Henderson family encounters a friendly Sasquatch and helps him evade a malicious hunter.

100000935.title: Paul
100000935.description: During a road trip to visit famous UFO sites, two sci-fi geeks encounter a wisecracking alien named Paul who is on the run from federal agents.

100000941.title: Mary and Max
100000941.description: Mary and Max are two misfits who become long-distance pen pals in this touching animated film about unlikely friendship and overcoming loneliness.

100001169.title: Why Stop Now?
100001169.description: When a piano prodigy tries to take his mother to rehab, a drug dealer takes them hostage and sweeps them into an adventure they were not expecting.

100001264.title: La Bella Y El Billonario (Doblado)
100001264.description: Addison trabaja con un multimillonario exigente como asistente en el lugar de su hermano y se encuentra desarrollando sentimientos por él.

100001403.title: Snow Dogs
100001403.description: When Miami dentist Ted Brooks inherits a team of rambunctious sled dogs, he has to learn the trade or lose his pack to a crusty mountain man.

100001406.title: Critters
100001406.description: After escaping from a maximum-security prison asteroid, a band of extraterrestrial flesh-eating criminals unwittingly land on planet Earth.

100001407.title: Flipped
100001407.description: “Somewhere between confusion and absolute terror,” 8th grader Bryce Loski begins to fall hard for the pesky girl who’s pined for him since age seven.

100001413.title: Matchstick Men
100001413.description: The streetwise teen daughter he never knew existed suddenly turns a neurotic con artist’s two-man team in small-time crime into a family business.

100001475.title: Doctor Dolittle
100001475.description: A workaholic doctor disrupts his family life and raises the concerns of his colleagues when he rediscovers his ability to communicate with animals.

100001476.title: RocketMan
100001476.description: An accident-prone computer programmer’s childhood dream comes true when he’s selected by NASA to join the first manned mission to Mars.

100001592.title: Tom & Jerry: The Movie
100001592.description: A desperate event planner conspires with Tom to catch his nemesis Jerry as the mouse wreaks havoc throughout a fancy Manhattan hotel during a wedding.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001600.title: Crazy Rich Asians
100001600.description: Rachel travels with her boyfriend Nick to a wedding in Singapore, where she finds out his family is extremely wealthy and not very eager to meet her.

100002070.title: Bad Cat
100002070.description: A profane house cat must deal with the arrival of his illegitimate son, an accidental killing, his owner's eviction and more within the course of a day of debauchery and mayhem.

100002072.title: Matt Rife: Only Fans
100002072.description: Comedian Matt Rife shares his unique perspective on the world in his debut special after ten years of performing stand-up comedy.

100002156.title: Men in Black
100002156.description: Tasked with policing extraterrestrial activities on Earth, two agents join forces to track down a dangerous alien intent upon galactic destruction.

100002157.title: Men in Black II
100002157.description: In order to save the planet from an alien seductress disguised as a supermodel, Agent J must find a way to restore his former partner’s memories.

100002158.title: Grown Ups
100002158.description: Five high school buddies reunite after 30 years to mourn the loss of their basketball coach and wrestle with the challenges of adulthood.

100002302.title: Men in Black 3
100002302.description: Agent J travels back in time to 1969, where he teams up with a younger version of Agent K to stop a time-hopping alien from destroying the future.

100002417.title: A Royal in Paradise
100002417.description: A pop fiction writer takes a post-breakup vacation where she runs into one of her fans and starts to fall for him—only to find out that he’s a Prince.

100002596.title: Keyholes Are for Peeping
100002596.description: In this funny parody of adult films, a momma’s boy gets a marriage counseling certificate and starts giving marital advice to couples in his building.

0300010104.title: LA's Finest
0300010104.description: A former DEA agent with a complicated past gets partnered with a working mom when she takes a new job as an LAPD detective in this Bad Boys spinoff.

0300008046.title: Sanford
0300008046.description: Redd Foxx is back as his classic "Sanford and Son" character, in the story of him taking on two partners and meeting a wealthy Beverly Hills widow.

0300000125.title: Welcome Back, Kotter
0300000125.description: This series follows teacher Gabe Kotter as he returns to his former high school to teach a remedial class of students known as the “Sweathogs.”

0300010304.title: My Cat from Hell
0300010304.description: Cat behaviorist Jackson Galaxy helps families on the verge of giving up their felines with taming techniques to reverse a host of headstrong habits.

0300010224.title: Scarecrow and Mrs. King
0300010224.description: A single mother in suburban Washington, D.C. discovers she has a talent for espionage work when she meets a dashing undercover agent.

0300004999.title: Garfield and Friends
0300004999.description: Lazy, lasagna-loving cat Garfield has fun adventures with his pal Odie and owner Jon.

0300008052.title: What's Happening!!
0300008052.description: Classic ‘70s series about L.A. high school journalist Raj and his best friends Rerun and Dwayne whose antics are never unseen by his nosy sister Dee.

0300007078.title: Soap
0300007078.description: A satire on soap operas, this zany comedy threw together a group of family members whose lives were larger than life and never dull! Stories take some bizarre and unexpected turns as the daily living of the wealthy Tate family and the blue-collar Campbell family unfold.

0300008580.title: Real Husbands of Hollywood
0300008580.description: Kevin Hart and his friends parody their own lives, where the pressures of spousal stardom are almost too much to handle, in this faux-reality satire.

0300008457.title: The Jeffersons
0300008457.description: Class, race, neighbors, family, and all kinds of clashes make for classic comedy in this beloved series about a family’s move on up to luxury living.

0300008639.title: The Steve Harvey Show
0300008639.description: Steve Harvey's sitcom from the WB network is classic '90s comedy about a musician-turned-teacher who teaches his unruly students a thing or three!

0300010076.title: Eight Is Enough
0300010076.description: This touching series follows a close-knit family as they face the hardships and challenges of the ups and downs of everyday life in a family of ten.

0300000124.title: Gilligan's Island
0300000124.description: Shipwrecked on an uncharted South Pacific island, seven castaways struggle to survive the outdoors—and each other—in this wacky classic comedy series.

0300006855.title: Scooby-Doo and Scrappy-Doo
0300006855.description: Everyone’s favorite mystery-solving Great Dane is here to find clues, along with a little help from his energetic nephew and four human companions.

0300007799.title: Blue Mountain State
0300007799.description: Three new athletes on a top college football team learn the extreme high and low of being among the chosen few who are worshiped and tested on campus.

0300009738.title: Sister, Sister
0300009738.description: Identical twins, separated at birth and adopted by different families, finally meet and try to bring their two very different parents together.

0300006868.title: Fantasy Island
0300006868.description: Dreams come true, for better or worse, in a tropical paradise, where a charming, enigmatic host and his diminutive assistant guide your magical visit.

0300006608.title: Bewitched
0300006608.description: The beloved TV series about a beautiful witch who marries an executive and starts a family as a housewife, much to the dismay of her powerful mother.

0300006856.title: The Flintstones
0300006856.description: Laugh along with the classic misadventures of two modern-day Stone Age families living amongst dinosaurs, doing their best in prehistoric times.

0300008079.title: The Bernie Mac Show
0300008079.description: Bernie Mac stars as a stand up comic who, alongside his businesswoman wife, must take in his sister's three kids while she's in rehab.

03006.title: Mr. Bean
03006.description: The simplest of daily tasks perplex and embarrass the beloved anti-hero, who always finds madcap, ingenious, and hilarious ways to solve his problems.

0300009046.title: Unspeakable
0300009046.description: YouTube sensation Nathan Graham pulls pranks, competes in wild challenges with friends, and collaborates with YouTube stars like Preston and ZHC.

0300004988.title: Fugget About It
0300004988.description: A former New York mobster joins the Witness Protection Program, which relocates him and his family, who must adjust to life in Saskatchewan, Canada.

0300006610.title: The Girls Next Door
0300006610.description: Go inside the Playboy Mansion and meet Holly, Kendra, and Bridget, Hugh Hefner’s girlfriends who fill their days with hilarious and sexy adventures.

0300010307.title: Toddlers & Tiaras
0300010307.description: This series takes viewers behind the scenes into the cutthroat—and often controversial—world of child beauty pageants, where winning is everything.

0300009281.title: Everybody Hates Chris
0300009281.description: Comedian Chris Rock narrates the hilarious, touching story of a teenager growing up as the eldest of three children in Brooklyn during the 1980s.

0300005101.title: Doc Martin
0300005101.description: A socially awkward doctor leaves London for a scenic village in Cornwall where he cares for the locals, becomes a part of their lives, and finds love.

0300000119.title: The Facts of Life
0300000119.description: Four teens, each with their own backgrounds and personalities, become inseparable friends when they’re brought together at Eastland Academy for girls.

0300008034.title: Larva
0300008034.description: Best buddies and fellow larvae Red and Yellow who have made their home in the gutter under a busy city street, play with objects that fall from above.

0300006874.title: The Nanny
0300006874.description: Fran Drescher stars as a jilted bride from Flushing, Queens who talks her way into becoming a nanny for a wealthy widower’s dysfunctional children.

0300006059.title: Kevin Can Wait
0300006059.description: A newly retired police officer has to reconsider his plans when his daughter announces she’s dropping out of college to support her fiancé.
